The Alliance isn't Predacon either. They're made of bots from both sides, as 
well as neutrals. Zardus doesn't have any symbols on his body.

GTG for now.

::Zardus::

Zardus looks down at Feline as she aproaches him, calmly watching as she 
traces a claw down his chest. His eyes follow her as she walks back to 
Skulletron, the Alliance commander looking at Skulletron to see his responce 
to the mission.
